CLASS demo DEFINITION.
  PUBLIC SECTION.
    CLASS-METHODS main.
ENDCLASS.

CLASS demo IMPLEMENTATION.

  METHOD main.
    DATA: lv_ts TYPE timestampl.
    CONVERT DATE sy-datum
            TIME sy-uzeit
            INTO TIME STAMP lv_ts
            TIME ZONE 'UTC+12'.
    IF sy-subrc IS INITIAL.
      WRITE lv_ts USING EDIT MASK '____-__-__T__:__:__.___Z' .
    ENDIF.
  ENDMETHOD.

ENDCLASS.

START-OF-SELECTION.
  demo=>main( ).





















